{
  "stem": "304.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the train used to stop once a day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It lasted about two and 1/2, three days, nights.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when they stopped the train, they opened the doors, but before they let the boys take out-- empty out the toilet buckets and bring in fresh water, they took two hostages from every car.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they threatened us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If you don't give us all the money and jewelry you are hiding, we will kill those two people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So the first time I encountered hostages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know if they killed people, because our two people always came back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we always heard shots ringing out, so I didn't know really what was going on somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, again, the train stops, and even if it was only two and 1/2 days, it sounded like two and 1/2 years.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It felt very long, the trip.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the train stopped, but it didn't open the doors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we're waiting and waiting for hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the night came and the night went, and, finally, they opened the doors from the cars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when the opened the doors, we went to the opening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Everybody was pushing to the opening to catch some fresh air because, by then, inside was really-- the stench, and the tiredness, and some old sick people even died in that car.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we wanted some fresh air and to look out where we were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think too hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in May.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was May-- beginning of May, 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans came in March, in April we were in the ghetto, in the beginning of May we left the ghetto, and they took us to camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
